Method Detail

setSelectNode

public void setSelectNode(int flags,
                          javax.media.j3d.Node node)
Associates the node with the specified select states. Any previous node association with these states will be lost.

Parameters:
flags - Select state flags (Feedback.SELECT_???).
node - Object shape, possibly a MultiShape. If null no shape will appear for the corresponding states.
